%h2 Code contribution

%h3 Set up The Library

%ol
	%li
		:markdown
			Clone the repository:  `git clone git@github.com:hybridgroup/artoo.git
	%li
		:markdown
			Optional Create a gemset: `rvm --create --rvmrc 1.9.3@artoo
	%li
		:markdown
			Install all the dependencies: bundle install

%h3 Tests

%p
	:markdown
		Make sure the tests pass: `rake test`

%h3 Submitting Code

%ul
	%li= link_to 'Review guidelines', '/documentation/contribute/guidelines'
	%li Fork the code.
	%li Create your feature branch (git checkout -b my-new-feature)
	%li Commit your changes (git commit -am 'Add some feature')
	%li Push to the branch (git push origin my-new-feature)
	%li
		Create a
		= link_to "new pull request" , "https://github.com/hybridgroup/artoo/compare?expand=1", target: :blank
